quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  60,1,"Eehey mon gooŇč…óin…ďe wote njaggire a√Ī…ďe mi e a√Ī…ďe mon heet…ďe ho…óon mberno e mum en gilli te ko…ďe yeddu…ďe goongo gar…óo o e mon, ho…ďe njaltina nelaa…óo e onon sabu tan on ngooŇč…óanii Alla joomi mon, tawde on njalti sabu jihaadi e laawol am e …óa…ďjude weluya am, ho…óon cuurtana…ďe kabaruuji juul…ďe ngam …ďe mbele mon, mbi…óa anndi ko cuu…óoton e ko …ďanngi…óon, kala e mon ba…ó…óo …óuum o majji laawol peewngol."
  60,2,"Si…ďe peewnatiima e mon …ďe ngonana mon a√Ī…ďe …ďe mberta juu…óe ma…ď…ďe e …óem…óe mu' en e mbaadi mbonndi …ďe nji…óiina nde ngonaton heeferee…ďe."
  60,3,"Nafatah on en…óameeje mon wona …ďi…ď…ďe mon √Īande darnga O seernda hakkunde mon Alla na yi'a ko ngolloton ko."
  60,4,"Woodanii on √Īeemtinirde mo∆ī∆īere e Ibraahiima e …ďeen wondu…ďe e mum nde …ďe mbi'i pellet ko min his…ďe e mon e ko ndewaton ko wona Alla ko, min njeddii on fee√Īi hakkunde men nga√Īngu e tikkere haa pooma haa ngooŇč…óinon Alla gooto o, si wona konngol Ibraahiima wonan'de baaba makko pellet ma mi yaafnano ma, mi alanaama hay hu'unde ka Alla, joomi amen min mbakkaliima e ma ko e ma min ndutti e ko e ma woni wattande."
  60,5,"joomi amen wota wa…ó min fitina wonan'de …ďeen yeddu…ďe, yaafa amen joomi amen pellet ko aan woni teddu…óo mbo fooletaake √Īee√Ī…óu…óo."